Package: scTernary
Title: Ternary plot analysis for single cell RNA-seq data
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Jinming", "Cheng", email="cheng.j@wehi.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3806-4694"))
Description: Ternary plot analysis is an easy way to identify and annotate cell 
    populations of single cell RNA-seq data. This package provides the functions
    for the ternary plot analysis.
